7. Be2 { White ignores the threat of ...Nxe4 and just goes on with their development. The idea is to prioritize rapid development in the good old romantic style. This was Nepomniachtchi's move, which he played in a blitz game against Dominguez in 2022. } Nxe4 { We of course take the pawn, also making use of the pin on White's Knight. } 
8. O-O { Continuing along with Nepo's idea. } Bxc3 
