17. Rb4 ( { The only move. After } 17.Bxc5 Qxc5 { White still retains two extra pawns. However, White will struggle to develop their Kingside pieces, and White's King will also be in danger. Therefore it is important for White to prioritize the development of their Kingside, even at the cost of sacrificing their Queen. } ) Nd3+ { We, of course, need to collect the material offered. } 
18. Qxd3 Rxd3 
